This Mod is a thing which adds Backpack which suits Player which is performing the role play as Guard of Whiterun to a game.
Backpack can be created in a blacksmith's shop.

Moreover, if it moves by a console command "coc qasmoke", it can be found on EnchantTeble.

This was created in the environment which translated the English-language edition into Japanese.
A certain fault may occur in the other environment.
